Ubuntu DESKTOP
-ctrl alt t
  *desktop
  sudo apt update             -
  sudo apt upgrade            +
  sudo apt install htop       + 
  sudo apt install nmap       +
  sudo apt install net-tools  +  //ifconfig'i yükler


